






@(1 = 1-9) O @wDN{An}, strengthen the foundations of the throne of life. @wRN{Rīm-@wDN{Sîn}}, may your name be called by a name of life; may he look upon you with favourable eyes, and pay attention to you.  @gap{1 line unclear}  May he determine a destiny of life as a fate for you. @wRN{Rīm-@wDN{Sîn}}, may you be beloved of @wDN{An}, and may your kingship endure forever. Great @wDN{An}, make him shepherd of the numerous people.



